<script language="javascript">
&lt;!--
	function jump_code()
	{
		var str=document.fund_search_code;
				
		if(document.getElementById("Select1").value == 18)
		{
			document.getElementById("Form1").action = "http://bar.hexun.com/PostSearchJJ.aspx?radiobutton=1&amp;sw="+document.getElementById("Text1").value;
		}
		else
		{
			document.getElementById("Form1").action = "http://funds.money.hexun.com/fundsdata/search/search_result.aspx";
		}
		if(eval(str).fund_code.value.length!=0)
		{
			eval(str).submit();
		}
		else
		{
			alert("请输入基金代码或基金名称！");
		}
	
	}
	function turnTo(event,element)
	{
		var code=event.keyCode;
		if(code == 13)
		{
			jump_code();
		}
	}
	function fundsearch()
	{
		var company = '';
		var organ = '';
		var type = '';
		var trustee = '';
		
		if(document.getElementById("company").value != '' &amp;&amp; document.getElementById("company").value != '--全部基金管理公司--')
		{
			company = document.getElementById("company").value;
		}
		if(document.getElementById("organ").value != '' &amp;&amp; document.getElementById("organ").value != '全部代销机构')
		{
			organ = document.getElementById("organ").value;
		}
		if(document.getElementById("type").value != '' &amp;&amp; document.getElementById("type").value != '全部投资类型')
		{
			type = document.getElementById("type").value;
		}
		if(document.getElementById("trustee").value != '' &amp;&amp; document.getElementById("trustee").value != '--全部基金托管银行--')
		{			
			trustee = document.getElementById("trustee").value;
		}
		
		if(company == "" &amp;&amp; organ == "" &amp;&amp; type == "" &amp;&amp; trustee == "")
		{
			alert('请选择查询条件');
		}
		else
		{
			window.open("/fundsdata07/search/data2.aspx?company=" + company + "&amp;organ="+ organ +"&amp;type=" + type + "&amp;trustee="+trustee);
		}
	}
--&gt;
</script>

<script language="javascript">
		var dropDiv=document.getElementById('dropDiv')
		function droplist(){
		if(dropDiv.style.display=='none'){
		   dropDiv.style.display='block';
		   dropDiv.style.height="0px"
		   var x=0;//dropDiv初始化高度
		   var y=parseInt(dropDiv.offsetHeight);//dropDiv层高度
		   var oSpeed=5;//滚动速度，数值越大滚动越慢
		   function dropScroll(){
		    if(x&lt;y){
		     dropDiv.style.height=x+"px";
		     x++;
		     var st=setTimeout(dropScroll,oSpeed)
		    }else{
		    clearTimeout(st);
		    }
		   }
		 dropScroll()
		}
		else
		dropDiv.style.display='none'
		}
		
		function closeDIV(ee){
			var ee=document.getElementById(ee);
			ee.style.display='none'
	  }
		</script>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
function coutLinkFrom(strId,mark,isId,p){
  var obj = null;
  if(isId) {
  if(!document.getElementById(strId)) return;
  obj = document.getElementById(strId);
  }
  else {
     var parent = (typeof p!='undefined' &amp;&amp; document.getElementById(p))?document.getElementById(p):document;
     var arr = parent.getElementsByTagName('*');
 var classesObj = [];
 for(var i=0,l=arr.length;i&lt;l;i++) {
   if(arr[i].className &amp;&amp; arr[i].className == strId) classesObj.push(arr[i]);
 }
 if(classesObj.length&gt;=1) obj = classesObj[0];
  }
  if(obj==null) return;
  var alist = obj.getElementsByTagName('a');
  var len = alist.length;
  for(var i=0;i&lt;len;i++) {
    if(alist[i].href) {
   alist[i].href = (alist[i].href.indexOf('?')!=-1)?(alist[i].href+'&amp;'+mark):(alist[i].href+'?'+mark);
}
  }
}
coutLinkFrom('jjjxmod','fromfunds=jjjx',false,'mainleft');
coutLinkFrom('yued','fromfunds=tjxd',true);
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
(function(){
  var reg = /^[http:\/\/\w|\w\.*\w|\w]+\.hexun\.com(\/|(\?[^\/]+)|\/index.html|\/index\-[\w]+.html)*$/;
  if(!reg.test(window.location.href)) {
    document.write('\x3Cscript type="text/javascript" src="http://img.hexun.com/base/version/hx_base.min1.1.js"&gt;\x3C/script&gt;'+'\x3Cscript type="text/javascript" src="http://img.hexun.com/share/hxShare2011.js"&gt;\x3C/script&gt;&lt;link href="http://img.hexun.com/share/hxShare2011.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet"  /&gt;');
    if(window.attachEvent) window.attachEvent('onload',function() {hxShare2011('');});
	if(window.addEventListener) window.addEventListener('load',function(){hxShare2011('');},false);
  }
})();
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
(function(){
	//全站通发广告
	var reg=/\/\d{9}(_\d+)?.(html|html\?\w*)$/;		
	if(reg.test(location.href)){
	    function allPages(){
		    var script = document.createElement('script');
			script.type = 'text/javascript';
			script.src = 'http://itv.hexun.com/lbi-html/ly/2011/allPages/tempAd.js';
			document.body.appendChild(script);			
		}
		if(window.attachEvent) window.attachEvent('onload',function() {allPages()});

})()
